item.title: Jennie Fans Can't Get Enough of Her New Single 'How U Like That'!
item.description: Jennie Fans Can’t Get Enough of Her New Single ‘How U Like That’! Jennie Kim, also known as Jennie from the K-pop group BLACKPINK, has just released her new single “How U Like That” This single has been taking the world by storm and has quickly become a favorite among fans Let’s take a closer look at why this single has been so popular Overview of Jennie’s new single “How U Like That” is a powerful and upbeat track that showcases Jennie’s strong vocals and creative style.
